Using recursion, this code becomes so easy and reliable :
In cpp,
Code :

long long int factorial(int N){
        //code here
        if(N==0) return 1;
        //if greater
        return N * factorial(N-1); //used recursion here
    }

Explanation :
0! = 1 (by default)
